explanation: Funds transferred to the DoD Rapid Prototyping Fund appropriations as required by section 828(d) of Public Law 114-92, the National Defense Authorization Act for FY 2016 (10 U.S.C. 2430 note) were proportionally allocated, as directed by section 8109 of division A of Public Law 115-245, the DoD Appropriations Act, 2019. This is base and Title IX OCO budget funding.
